und the world prior to coming to yale university dr zimmerman was a program manager at the us environmental protection agency where she established the national sustainable design competition p people prosperity and planet award which has engaged design teams from hundreds of universities across the us  dr zimmerman earned her bs from the university of virginia and her phd jointly from the school of engineering and the school of natural resources and environment at the university of michigan education university of virginia bs civil environmental engineering university of michigan ms environmental and water resource engineering university of michigan phd environmental engineering  natural resource policy previous   pegasus partners v lp  ceo founder businessman  profile directorpedianet  list of ceos founders board members and company directors pegasus partners v lp check out list of companies and businesses related to pegasus partners v lp find out pegasus partners v lp address and contact details view other people related to pegasus partners v lp  coworkers colleagues companions etc address co pegasus capital advisors lp  river road cos cob  ct companies related to pegasus partners v lp cikcompany namepositioncompany addresslighting science group corp division road suite  west warwick  pegasus partners v lp on the web persons related to pegasus partners v lp  lighting science group corpnamepositioncitycooper andrewsatellite beachadvisory partners ardsley owner stamfordrobert e bachmandirector dallasrobert e bachmandirector dallasrobert e bachmandirector dallasrobert e bachmandirector dallasrobert e bachmandirector dallasrobert e bachmandirector dallasrobert e bachmandirector satellite beachjason patrick barleysouthlakeandrew becksatellite beachedward d bednarcikchief executive officer melbournedavid arthur belldirector david arthur belldirector satellite beachdavid arthur bellnew yorkdavid arthur belldirector new yorkdavid arthur belldirector new yorkdavid arthur 